content.html: If you sent me a message and I never responded, Just know that I stress about it every single day because I haven’t figured out how to respond so I feel immense guilt every time I see that unanswered message… OR I’ve forgotten that your message (and you) even exist.
content.value:
If you sent me a message and I never responded,

Just know that I stress about it every single day because I haven’t figured out how to respond so I feel immense guilt every time I see that unanswered message…

OR I’ve forgotten that your message (and you) even exist.
